{"ts":"2026-06-26T17:12:33.391Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Confirming Completeness & Next Step**\n\nI'm feeling really good about this! It's all clicking, and I'm ready to proceed with writing that ultra-premium `BlueprintGenerator.tsx` component. Just want to take a quick peek around to ensure I have all the necessary files on hand, especially that `BlueprintAnswers` schema and options within `lib`.\n\n\n**Designing the Rail & Layout**\n\nI've got the overall structure for the `BlueprintGenerator.tsx` component sorted! Now, I'm meticulously designing a top progress rail with six steps, each with a progress bar, checkmarks, and glowing indicators. It'll be a beautiful way to show which step is active. The live synthesis engine panel layout will be a grid. On desktop, the active step form container will span three columns, with the \"GFF Real-Time Synthesis Engine\" sidebar taking the remaining column. It's looking strategic, bespoke, and expensive!\n\n\n**Defining the Sidebar Design**\n\nI've been envisioning the sidebar! It's going to be a sticky container with a dark cyber-border and a pulsing blue header displaying `SYS_STATUS: ACTIVE`. Inside, it will list the compiled parameters, updating live as users complete each step! The layout and parameters include sector, scale, strategy, maturity, infrastructure, leadership, roadblock, and portal. I'm keen on making it very engaging!\n\n\n**Expanding the Options**\n\nI'm now expanding the options for the first step. I plan to use a simple dropdown to display a grid of six custom cards with inline SVG icons representing different sectors. These include Banking, Retail, Healthcare, Manufacturing, Tech, and Other Services. I want the user to be able to save their selection, with the chosen card gaining a glowing border and a checkmark. Next, I'm thinking about company size, which will be a grid of four cards, followed by budget and geography in a secondary layout.\n\n\n**Refining Input Styles**\n\nI'm now refining the input styles, leaning towards elegant select pills for geography selection from North America, Europe, APAC, LATAM, and Global. For Step 2, I'm defining a grid of seven gorgeous priority cards, with hover effects and selection tracking. In Step 3, a vertical timeline of six maturity stages will be the design, each having a stage label and description.\n\n\n**Defining Step 4 & 5**\n\nI've just defined Step 4 and 5. For Infrastructure & Governance (Step 4), I'll use option cards for data readiness and leadership commitment. Step 5 focuses on the \"Core Organizational Challenge\" with high-contrast pills or horizontal cards to select from categories. The selections affect `answers.aiJourney`. The options include a number of options that focus on implementation concerns.\n\n\n**Defining Challenge Input**\n\nI'm now designing the last two steps. For \"Custom Challenge Detail\" I'm envisioning a spacious text area with rich dark styling and a glowing focus border. I'll include a character counter and a helpful placeholder showing users what's expected. For the final step, \"Secure Portal Gate,\" I'm planning an enterprise email input field with an envelope icon, followed by an OTP PIN verification.\n\n\n**Finalizing Blueprint Generation**\n\nNow I'm finalizing the final step: the \"Secure Portal Gate.\" I'm envisioning an enterprise email input and OTP verification. A premium 6-character PIN box is key for bypassing the verification. I'm coding the \"Verify & Build Blueprint\" button with a pulsing glow, as well. I'm going to create a temporary backup and carefully write the whole file content into `BlueprintGenerator.tsx` using `editor`. It's going to be about 600-700 lines, so I'll write it in a very structured way. I'm planning out every single line of the component, with no placeholders! I've also listed the CSS classes to keep the design consistent.\n\n\n**Adding Animation & Styling**\n\nI'm now thinking about animations and custom styling! I'm planning to inject inline CSS with `<style jsx>` or a regular `<style>` tag for beautiful CSS keyframe animations, specifically for elements like `.animate-fade-in-up`, `.animate-glow`, and `.animate-border-pulse`. This should add a lot of flair to the design.\n\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T17:12:33.398Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"tvy9xffe","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/components/sections/BlueprintGenerator.tsx","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport { useState, useEffect } from \"react\";\nimport {\n  BlueprintAnswers,\n  industryOptions,\n  companySizeOptions,\n  priorityOptions,\n  aiJourneyOptions,\n  dataReadinessOptions,\n  leadershipOptions,\n  challengeOptions,\n  budgetOptions,\n  geographyOptions,\n  calculateBlueprintScore,\n  getScoreCategory,\n  getRecommendedOpportunities,\n  getRecommendedSolution,\n  getExpectedImpact,\n} from \"@/lib/blueprint-data\";\n\nconst compilingMessages = [\n  \"Analyzing industry process patterns...\",\n  \"Calculating AI Maturity Index...\",\n  \"Compiling dynamic multi-agent DAG topologies...\",\n  \"Synthesizing 90-day enterprise execution roadmap...\",\n  \"Running compliance audit baseline checks...\"\n];\n\nexport default function BlueprintGenerator() {\n  // Wizard state (Steps 1 to 6 are inputs, Step 7 is report)\n  const [step, setStep] = useState(1);\n  const [answers, setAnswers] = useState<BlueprintAnswers>({\n    industry: \"\",\n    companySize: \"\",\n    topPriorities: [],\n    aiJourney: \"\",\n    dataReadiness: \"\",\n    leadershipCommitment: \"\",\n    biggestChallenge: \"\",\n    email: \"\",\n    otp: \"\",\n    budget: \"\",\n    geography: \"\",\n  });\n\n  const [customChallengeText, setCustomChallengeText] = useState(\"\");\n\n  // Verification states\n  const [otpSent, setOtpSent] = useState(false);\n  const [enteredOtp, setEnteredOtp] = useState(\"\");\n  const [otpError, setOtpError] = useState(\"\");\n  const [isCompiling, setIsCompiling] = useState(false);\n  const [compilingStep, setCompilingStep] = useState(0);\n  const [reportGenerated, setReportGenerated] = useState(false);\n  \n  // Validation errors\n  const [error, setError] = useState(\"\");\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!isCompiling) return;\n    const interval = setInterval(() => {\n      setCompilingStep((prev) => {\n        if (prev < compilingMessages.length - 1) {\n          return prev + 1;\n        } else {\n          clearInterval(interval);\n          setIsCompiling(false);\n          setReportGenerated(true);\n          setStep(7); // Show high-fidelity report\n          return prev;\n        }\n      });\n    }, 600);\n    return () => clearInterval(interval);\n  }, [isCompiling]);\n\n  // Handle priority multi-selection (max 3)\n  const handlePriorityToggle = (val: string) => {\n    setError(\"\");\n    const current = [...answers.topPriorities];\n    if (current.includes(val)) {\n      setAnswers({\n        ...answers,\n        topPriorities: current.filter((x) => x !== val),\n      });\n    } else {\n      if (current.length >= 3) {\n        setError(\"Maximum 3 strategic priorities can be selected.\");\n        return;\n      }\n      setAnswers({\n        ...answers,\n        topPriorities: [...current, val],\n      });\n    }\n  };\n\n  // Step-by-step validations\n  const validateAndNext = () => {\n    setError(\"\");\n    if (step === 1) {\n      if (!answers.industry) {\n        setError(\"Please select an industry vertical to continue.\");\n        return;\n      }\n      if (!answers.companySize) {\n        setError(\"Please select your company scale.\");\n        return;\n      }\n      setStep(2);\n    } else if (step === 2) {\n      if (answers.topPriorities.length === 0) {\n        setError(\"Please select at least 1 strategic priority (maximum 3).\");\n        return;\n      }\n      setStep(3);\n    } else if (step === 3) {\n      if (!answers.aiJourney) {\n        setError(\"Please select your organization's AI journey stage.\");\n        return;\n      }\n      setStep(4);\n    } else if (step === 4) {\n      if (!answers.dataReadiness) {\n        setError(\"Please select your current data readiness level.\");\n        return;\n      }\n      if (!answers.leadershipCommitment) {\n        setError(\"Please specify your leadership alignment tier.\");\n        return;\n      }\n      setStep(5);\n    } else if (step === 5) {\n      if (!answers.biggestChallenge) {\n        setError(\"Please select a primary challenge category.\");\n        return;\n      }\n      if (!customChallengeText || customChallengeText.trim().length < 10) {\n        setError(\"Please describe your roadblock in at least 10 characters.\");\n        return;\n      }\n      setStep(6);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handleBack = () => {\n    setError(\"\");\n    if (step > 1) {\n      setStep(step - 1);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const requestOtp = () => {\n    setError(\"\");\n    if (!answers.email || !answers.email.includes(\"@\") || answers.email.length < 5) {\n      setError(\"Please enter a valid enterprise email address.\");\n      return;\n    }\n    setOtpSent(true);\n  };\n\n  const verifyOtpAndGenerate = () => {\n    setOtpError(\"\");\n    if (!enteredOtp) {\n      setOtpError(\"Please enter the verification PIN.\");\n      return;\n    }\n    if (enteredOtp.length < 4) {\n      setOtpError(\"PIN code must be at least 4 digits.\");\n      return;\n    }\n    setIsCompiling(true);\n  };\n\n  // Calculate score & reports\n  const score = calculateBlueprintScore(answers);\n  const category = getScoreCategory(score);\n  const opportunities = getRecommendedOpportunities(answers.industry);\n  const solution = getRecommendedSolution(answers.biggestChallenge);\n  const impact = getExpectedImpact(answers.topPriorities);\n\n  // Industry custom icon mapping\n  const getIndustryIcon = (val: string) => {\n    switch (val) {\n      case \"Banking\":\n        return (\n          <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#087DF3]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\">\n            <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.5M4.5 21V10.5M12 9h.008v.008H12V9zM12 12h.008v.008H12V12z\" />\n          </svg>\n        );\n      case \"Retail\":\n        return (\n          <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#E98828]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\">\n            <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15.75 10.5V6a3.75 3.75 0 10-7.5 0v4.5m11.356-1.993l1.263 12c.07.665-.45 1.243-1.119 1.243H4.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.12-1.243l1.264-12A1.125 1.125 0 015.513 7.5h12.974c.576 0 1.059.435 1.119 1.007zM8.625 10.5a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm7.5 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0z\" />\n          </svg>\n        );\n      case \"Healthcare\":\n        return (\n          <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\">\n            <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z\" />\n          </svg>\n        );\n      case \"Manufacturing\":\n        return (\n          <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-purple-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\">\n            <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4.5 12a7.5 7.5 0 0015 0m-15 0a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0m-15 0H3m16.5 0H21m-1.5 0H12m-8.457 3.077l1.41-.513m14.095-5.13l1.41-.513M5.106 17.785l1.15-.827m11.379-8.16l1.15-.827M8.14 21.27l.707-1.03m7.45-.808l.707-1.03M12 3v1.5m0 15V21m-3.077-16.543l.513 1.41m5.13 14.095l.513 1.41M17.785 5.106l-.827 1.15m-8.16 11.379l-.827 1.15M21.27 8.14l-1.03.707m-.808 7.45l-1.03.707\" />\n          </svg>\n        );\n      case \"Tech\":\n        return (\n          <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#087DF3]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\">\n            <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M17.25 6.75L22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3l-4.5 16.5\" />\n          </svg>\n        );\n      default:\n        return (\n          <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\">\n            <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9s2.015-9 4.5-9m0 0a9.003 9.003 0 018.313 12.455M12 3a9.003 9.003 0 00-8.313 12.455\" />\n          </svg>\n        );\n    }\n  };\n\n  // Steps labels & helpers\n  const stepTitles = [\n    \"Organization\",\n    \"Priorities\",\n    \"AI Journey\",\n    \"Governance\",\n    \"Core Roadblock\",\n    \"Verification\"\n  ];\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"w-full max-w-[1550px] mx-auto space-y-8 relative px-2\">\n      <style>{`\n        @keyframes slideUp {\n          from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }\n          to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n        @keyframes pulseGlow {\n          0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(8, 125, 243, 0.15); }\n          50% { box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(8, 125, 243, 0.35); }\n        }\n        .anim-slide-up {\n          animation: slideUp 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;\n        }\n        .anim-pulse-glow {\n          animation: pulseGlow 2.5s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n      `}</style>\n\n      {/* Top Header & Title */}\n      <div className=\"p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071426] via-[#050505] to-[#120720] relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\">\n        <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none\" />\n        <div className=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[200px] h-[200px] bg-purple-500/5 rounded-full blur-[80px] pointer-events-none\" />\n        \n        <div className=\"relative z-10\">\n          <div className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-[#087DF3]/30 bg-[#087DF3]/5 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#087DF3] uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 font-mono\">\n            <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#087DF3] animate-pulse\" />\n            SECURE SELF-ASSESSMENT ENGINE\n          </div>\n          <h2 className=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-[42px] leading-tight font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-slate-100 to-slate-400\">\n            Sovereign Enterprise AI Blueprint Generator\n          </h2>\n          <p className=\"mt-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/65 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed\">\n            Formulate your tailored operating model, target multi-agent DAG architectures, and synthesized 90-day execution roadmap built on standard GFF AI baselines.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Progress Indicators / Navigation Rail */}\n      {step < 7 && (\n        <div className=\"w-full bg-[#030712]/60 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-4 md:p-6 shadow-md\">\n          {/* Progress Rail Desktop */}\n          <div className=\"hidden md:flex items-center justify-between relative\">\n            <div className=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-white/5 -translate-y-1/2 z-0\" />\n            <div \n              className=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#087DF3] to-[#E98828] -translate-y-1/2 z-0 transition-all duration-500\"\n              style={{ width: `${((step - 1) / 5) * 100}%` }}\n            />\n            \n            {stepTitles.map((title, idx) => {\n              const num = idx + 1;\n              const isActive = step === num;\n              const isCompleted = step > num;\n              \n              return (\n                <div key={title} className=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center\">\n                  <div \n                    className={`w-9 h-9 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold font-mono transition-all duration-300 ${\n                      isActive \n                        ? \"border-2 border-[#087DF3] bg-black text-white shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(8,125,243,0.4)] scale-110\" \n                        : isCompleted \n                        ? \"border border-emerald-500 bg-emerald-950/40 text-emerald-400\" \n                        : \"border border-white/10 bg-[#0a0f1d] text-white/40\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    {isCompleted ? \"✓\" : `0${num}`}\n                  </div>\n                  <span className={`text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold mt-2 transition-all duration-300 ${\n                    isActive ? \"text-[#087DF3] font-bold\" : isCompleted ? \"text-emerald-400/80\" : \"text-white/30\"\n                  }`}>\n                    {title}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n              );\n            })}\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Progress Mobile View */}\n          <div className=\"md:hidden flex flex-col gap-2\">\n            <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-xs\">\n              <span className=\"text-white/40 uppercase font-bold font-mono tracking-wider\">Assessment Status</span>\n              <span className=\"text-[#087DF3] font-bold font-mono\">Step {step} of 6</span>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"w-full h-1.5 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n              <div \n                className=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#087DF3] to-[#E98828] transition-all duration-500\"\n                style={{ width: `${(step / 6) * 100}%` }}\n              />\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"text-[11px] text-white/70 italic\">\n              Active Focus: <span className=\"font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider ml-1\">{stepTitles[step - 1]}</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* Main Grid: Steps on Left, Real-Time Synthesis Sidebar on Right */}\n      {step < 7 ? (\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 items-start\">\n          \n          {/* Active Wizard Step Form */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/45 backdrop-blur-md p-6 md:p-8 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden min-h-[480px] flex flex-col justify-between anim-slide-up\">\n            <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-[#087DF3]\" />\n            \n            <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n              {/* Step 1: Organization Profiling */}\n              {step === 1 && (\n                <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 className=\"text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      <span className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[#087DF3]\">01</span>\n                      Organization Context & Scale\n                    </h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 mt-1\">\n                      Identify your vertical sector and operational volume to align the AI execution node parameters.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"space-y-5\">\n                    {/* Industry Custom Cards */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <label className=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70\">\n                        Industry Vertical <span className=\"text-[#087DF3] font-bold\">*</span>\n                      </label>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n                        {industryOptions.map((opt) => {\n                          const isSelected = answers.industry === opt.value;\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={opt.value}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => {\n                                setError(\"\");\n                                setAnswers({ ...answers, industry: opt.value });\n                              }}\n                              className={`p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition duration-200 flex flex-col gap-3 group relative ${\n                                isSelected\n                                  ? \"border-[#087DF3] bg-[#087DF3]/10 text-white shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(8,125,243,0.15)]\"\n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] text-white/70 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.04]\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              {isSelected && (\n                                <span className=\"absolute top-3 right-3 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-[#087DF3] text-[9px] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold\">✓</span>\n                              )}\n                              <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg bg-white/5 w-fit group-hover:bg-white/10 transition\">\n                                {getIndustryIcon(opt.value)}\n                              </div>\n                              <span className=\"text-xs font-bold leading-tight\">{opt.label}</span>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* Company Scale Grid */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-2 pt-2\">\n                      <label className=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70\">\n                        Organization Scale <span className=\"text-[#087DF3] font-bold\">*</span>\n                      </label>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n                        {companySizeOptions.map((opt) => {\n                          const isSelected = answers.companySize === opt.value;\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={opt.value}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => {\n                                setError(\"\");\n                                setAnswers({ ...answers, companySize: opt.value });\n                              }}\n                              className={`p-3.5 rounded-xl border text-center transition duration-200 relative ${\n                                isSelected\n                                  ? \"border-[#087DF3] bg-[#087DF3]/15 text-white\"\n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] text-white/70 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.04]\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <div className=\"text-xs font-extrabold\">{opt.label}</div>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* Optional Budget & Geography */}\n                    <div className=\"pt-4 border-t border-white/5 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                      <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                        <label className=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/40 block\">\n                          Target Budget Range <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/20 font-mono font-normal\">(Optional)</span>\n                        </label>\n                        <select\n                          value={answers.budget}\n                          onChange={(e) => setAnswers({ ...answers, budget: e.target.value })}\n                          className=\"w-full h-[44px] rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/65 px-3 text-xs text-white/75 focus:border-[#087DF3] outline-none transition\"\n                        >\n                          <option value=\"\">-- No target budget set --</option>\n                          {budgetOptions.map((o) => (\n                            <option key={o.value} value={o.value}>{o.label}</option>\n                          ))}\n                        </select>\n                      </div>\n\n                      <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                        <label className=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/40 block\">\n                          Primary Geography <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/20 font-mono font-normal\">(Optional)</span>\n                        </label>\n                        <select\n                          value={answers.geography}\n                          onChange={(e) => setAnswers({ ...answers, geography: e.target.value })}\n                          className=\"w-full h-[44px] rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/65 px-3 text-xs text-white/75 focus:border-[#087DF3] outline-none transition\"\n                        >\n                          <option value=\"\">-- Global Operation --</option>\n                          {geographyOptions.map((o) => (\n                            <option key={o.value} value={o.value}>{o.label}</option>\n                          ))}\n                        </select>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* Step 2: Strategic Priorities */}\n              {step === 2 && (\n                <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 className=\"text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      <span className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[#087DF3]\">02</span>\n                      Strategic Priorities (Select Up to 3)\n                    </h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 mt-1\">\n                      Choose which business optimization vectors GFF agents should address first. This calibrates your business needs coefficient.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3 pt-2\">\n                    {priorityOptions.map((opt) => {\n                      const isSelected = answers.topPriorities.includes(opt.value);\n                      return (\n                        <button\n                          key={opt.value}\n                          type=\"button\"\n                          onClick={() => handlePriorityToggle(opt.value)}\n                          className={`p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition duration-200 flex justify-between items-center group relative ${\n                            isSelected\n                              ? \"border-[#087DF3] bg-[#087DF3]/15 text-white\"\n                              : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-white/70 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.03]\"\n                          }`}\n                        >\n                          <div className=\"space-y-1 pr-4\">\n                            <span className=\"text-xs md:text-sm font-bold leading-tight block\">{opt.label}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <span className={`w-4 h-4 rounded-full border flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 ${\n                            isSelected ? \"border-[#087DF3] bg-[#087DF3]\" : \"border-white/20\"\n                          }`}>\n                            {isSelected && <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white\">✓</span>}\n                          </span>\n                        </button>\n                      );\n                    })}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* Step 3: AI Maturity Stage */}\n              {step === 3 && (\n                <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 className=\"text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      <span className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[#087DF3]\">03</span>\n                      Current AI Adoption Stage\n                    </h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 mt-1\">\n                      Assess your existing experience to customize the operational rollout stages and roadmap learning-curves.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 pt-2\">\n                    {aiJourneyOptions.map((opt, idx) => {\n                      const isSelected = answers.aiJourney === opt.value;\n                      \n                      // Rich helper descriptions for premium look\n                      const journeyDescriptions = [\n                        \"No AI implementations in production; currently surveying options.\",\n                        \"Initial workshops completed; assessing specific operational pilots.\",\n                        \"Isolated, active pilot workflows or custom isolated GPT instances.\",\n                        \"Multi-department pipelines; production-ready systems scaling.\",\n                        \"Agent-centric models are standard for operations and scheduling.\",\n                        \"Workflows are automated by default with human-in-the-loop nodes.\"\n                      ];\n\n                      return (\n                        <button\n                          key={opt.value}\n                          type=\"button\"\n                          onClick={() => {\n                            setError(\"\");\n                            setAnswers({ ...answers, aiJourney: opt.value });\n                          }}\n                          className={`p-4 rounded-xl border text-left transition duration-200 flex flex-col gap-1 relative ${\n                            isSelected\n                              ? \"border-[#087DF3] bg-[#087DF3]/15 text-white\"\n                              : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-white/70 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.03]\"\n                          }`}\n                        >\n                          <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-[#087DF3]\">STAGE 0{idx + 1}</span>\n                            {isSelected && <span className=\"text-xs text-[#087DF3] font-bold\">● ACTIVE</span>}\n                          </div>\n                          <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1\">{opt.label}</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 mt-1 leading-normal\">{journeyDescriptions[idx] || \"\"}</span>\n                        </button>\n                      );\n                    })}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* Step 4: Data and Leadership */}\n              {step === 4 && (\n                <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 className=\"text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      <span className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[#087DF3]\">04</span>\n                      Infrastructure & Leadership Buy-In\n                    </h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 mt-1\">\n                      Calibrate your backend readiness coefficient alongside institutional alignment parameters.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"space-y-5\">\n                    {/* Data Readiness Select Grid */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <label className=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70\">\n                        Primary Data Readiness <span className=\"text-[#087DF3] font-bold\">*</span>\n                      </label>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n                        {dataReadinessOptions.map((opt, idx) => {\n                          const isSelected = answers.dataReadiness === opt.value;\n                          const labels = [\"Highly Fragmented\", \"Partially Connected\", \"Mostly Integrated\", \"Fully Integrated\"];\n                          const descs = [\"Isolated CSVs & databases\", \"Basic REST APIs established\", \"Centralized data-lakes\", \"Unified vector mesh networks\"];\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={opt.value}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => {\n                                setError(\"\");\n                                setAnswers({ ...answers, dataReadiness: opt.value });\n                              }}\n                              className={`p-3.5 rounded-xl border text-left transition duration-200 flex flex-col gap-1 ${\n                                isSelected\n                                  ? \"border-[#087DF3] bg-[#087DF3]/15 text-white\"\n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-white/70 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.03]\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <span className=\"text-xs font-extrabold text-white\">{labels[idx]}</span>\n                              <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 leading-tight\">{descs[idx]}</span>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* Leadership Commitment Grid */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-2 pt-2\">\n                      <label className=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70\">\n                        Leadership Alignment <span className=\"text-[#087DF3] font-bold\">*</span>\n                      </label>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n                        {leadershipOptions.map((opt, idx) => {\n                          const isSelected = answers.leadershipCommitment === opt.value;\n                          const labels = [\"Not Discussed\", \"Exploring\", \"Budget Approved\", \"Executive Mandate\"];\n                          const descs = [\"No core initiative\", \"Assessing feasibility\", \"Sovereign funding ready\", \"Top-down directive\"];\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={opt.value}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => {\n                                setError(\"\");\n                                setAnswers({ ...answers, leadershipCommitment: opt.value });\n                              }}\n                              className={`p-3.5 rounded-xl border text-left transition duration-200 flex flex-col gap-1 ${\n                                isSelected\n                                  ? \"border-[#087DF3] bg-[#087DF3]/15 text-white\"\n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-white/70 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.03]\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              <span className=\"text-xs font-extrabold text-white\">{labels[idx]}</span>\n                              <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 leading-tight\">{descs[idx]}</span>\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* Step 5: Challenge Select & Textarea */}\n              {step === 5 && (\n                <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 className=\"text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      <span className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-white/5 text-[#087DF3]\">05</span>\n                      Your Primary Strategic Challenge\n                    </h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 mt-1\">\n                      GFF AI adapts recommended software meshes based on specific technological, compliance, or financial bottlenecks.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"space-y-5\">\n                    {/* Challenge Category Selector Pills */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <label className=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70\">\n                        Primary Bottleneck Category <span className=\"text-[#087DF3] font-bold\">*</span>\n                      </label>\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-2.5\">\n                        {challengeOptions.map((opt) => {\n                          const isSelected = answers.biggestChallenge === opt.value;\n                          const cleanLabel = opt.label.split(\" & \").pop()?.split(\" Constraint\").shift() || opt.label;\n                          return (\n                            <button\n                              key={opt.value}\n                              type=\"button\"\n                              onClick={() => {\n                                setError(\"\");\n                                setAnswers({ ...answers, biggestChallenge: opt.value });\n                              }}\n                              className={`p-2.5 rounded-lg border text-center transition duration-200 text-xs font-bold leading-tight ${\n                                isSelected\n                                  ? \"border-[#087DF3] bg-[#087DF3]/15 text-white shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(8,125,243,0.1)]\"\n                                  : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-white/60 hover:border-white/10 hover:text-white/80\"\n                              }`}\n                            >\n                              {cleanLabel}\n                            </button>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* Elaborative Textarea */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                        <label className=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70\">\n                          Describe your roadblock in detail <span className=\"text-[#087DF3] font-bold\">*</span>\n                        </label>\n                        <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30\">{customChallengeText.length} chars (min 10)</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <textarea\n                        value={customChallengeText}\n                        onChange={(e) => {\n                          setError(\"\");\n                          setCustomChallengeText(e.target.value);\n                        }}\n                        placeholder=\"E.g., We have massive legacy databases in SQL and SAP, but no unified knowledge graph. We want to automate invoice ingestion but are worried about security, token limits, and compliance...\"\n                        className=\"w-full h-32 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/65 p-4 text-xs md:text-sm text-white focus:border-[#087DF3] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#087DF3]/20 outline-none transition resize-none leading-relaxed\"\n                      />\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* Step 6: Email and OTP Gateway Placeholder */}\n              {step === 6 && (\n                <div className=\"space-y-6 max-w-[540px] mx-auto w-full py-2\">\n                  <div className=\"text-center space-y-2\">\n                    <div className=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#087DF3]/10 border border-[#087DF3]/20 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto text-[#087DF3]\">\n                      <svg className=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\">\n                        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z\" />\n                      </svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 className=\"text-lg font-bold text-white\">Sovereign Portal Gate</h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 max-w-sm mx-auto leading-relaxed\">\n                      Authorize access via secure enterprise credential checkpoint to synthesize your interactive topology roadmap.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"space-y-4 pt-2\">\n                    {/* Enterprise Email field */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <label className=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70 block\">Enterprise Email Address</label>\n                      <input\n                        type=\"email\"\n                        disabled={otpSent}\n                        value={answers.email}\n                        onChange={(e) => {\n                          setError(\"\");\n                          setAnswers({ ...answers, email: e.target.value });\n                        }}\n                        placeholder=\"yourname@enterprise.com\"\n                        className=\"w-full h-[46px] rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/50 px-4 text-xs md:text-sm text-white focus:border-[#087DF3] outline-none transition disabled:opacity-40\"\n                      />\n                    </div>\n\n                    {!otpSent ? (\n                      <button\n                        type=\"button\"\n                        onClick={requestOtp}\n                        className=\"w-full h-[46px] rounded-lg bg-[#087DF3] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white hover:bg-[#087DF3]/90 hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(8,125,243,0.35)] transition-all mt-2\"\n                      >\n                        Request Access PIN\n                      </button>\n                    ) : (\n                      <div className=\"space-y-4 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 anim-slide-up\">\n                        {/* Clearly Labeled Simulated OTP Code Checkpoint */}\n                        <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/20 bg-amber-500/5 space-y-2\">\n                          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                            <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500 animate-pulse\" />\n                            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-amber-500 font-mono tracking-wider uppercase\">Simulated Node</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">\n                            No external emails will be dispatched. Use the simulated PIN below to authorize immediately:\n                          </p>\n                          <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center py-1 px-3 rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10\">\n                            <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-mono font-bold\">Suggested OTP:</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-xs font-mono font-extrabold text-[#087DF3] tracking-widest\">123456</span>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n\n                        {/* PIN Code Box */}\n                        <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                          <label className=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70 block\">Enter One-Time PIN (OTP)</label>\n                          <input\n                            type=\"text\"\n                            maxLength={6}\n                            value={enteredOtp}\n                            onChange={(e) => {\n                              setError(\"\");\n                              setEnteredOtp(e.target.value.replace(/\\D/g, \"\"));\n                            }}\n                            placeholder=\"Enter 6-digit PIN\"\n                            className=\"w-full h-[46px] rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/50 px-4 text-xs sm:text-sm text-center tracking-[0.4em] font-mono text-white focus:border-[#087DF3] outline-none transition\"\n                          />\n                          {otpError && <p className=\"text-[10px] text-red-400 font-bold\">{otpError}</p>}\n                        </div>\n\n                        <button\n                          type=\"button\"\n                          onClick={verifyOtpAndGenerate}\n                          className=\"w-full h-[46px] rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-all mt-2\"\n                        >\n                          Verify PIN & Generate Roadmap\n                        </button>\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              )}\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Bottom Controls / Error Display */}\n            <div className=\"mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-between items-center relative z-10\">\n              <div className=\"h-6\">\n                {error && (\n                  <p className=\"text-[11px] md:text-xs text-red-400 font-bold flex items-center gap-1.5 anim-slide-up\">\n                    <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-400\" />\n                    {error}\n                  </p>\n                )}\n              </div>\n              \n              <div className=\"flex gap-3 ml-auto w-full sm:w-auto justify-end\">\n                {step > 1 && (\n                  <button\n                    type=\"button\"\n                    onClick={handleBack}\n                    className=\"px-5 h-[42px] rounded-lg border border-white/10 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white hover:bg-white/5 hover:border-white/20 transition-all\"\n                  >\n                    Back\n                  </button>\n                )}\n                {step < 6 && (\n                  <button\n                    type=\"button\"\n                    onClick={validateAndNext}\n                    className=\"px-8 h-[44px] rounded-lg bg-[#087DF3] text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white hover:bg-[#1a88f5] hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(8,125,243,0.35)] transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n                  >\n                    Continue\n                  </button>\n                )}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Real-Time Parameter Synthesis Sidebar */}\n          <div className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030712]/40 backdrop-blur-md p-5 shadow-xl space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-white/40 tracking-wider\">REAL-TIME SYNTHESIS</span>\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#087DF3] animate-ping\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-extrabold text-[#087DF3]\">SYS_READY</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-4 font-mono text-[10px] leading-relaxed\">\n              {/* Sector */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/30 block uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">01_VERTICAL_SECTOR</span>\n                {answers.industry ? (\n                  <span className=\"text-white font-bold block truncate text-[11px] glow-text\">{answers.industry}</span>\n                ) : (\n                  <span className=\"text-white/25 italic block\">[PENDING_SELECTION]</span>\n                )}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Company Scale */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/30 block uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">02_OPERATIONAL_SCALE</span>\n                {answers.companySize ? (\n                  <span className=\"text-[#E98828] font-bold block truncate text-[11px]\">{answers.companySize} Employees</span>\n                ) : (\n                  <span className=\"text-white/25 italic block\">[PENDING_SELECTION]</span>\n                )}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Priorities */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/30 block uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">03_AGENT_TARGETS</span>\n                {answers.topPriorities.length > 0 ? (\n                  <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 pt-1\">\n                    {answers.topPriorities.map((p) => (\n                      <span key={p} className=\"px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-[#087DF3]/15 text-[#087DF3] text-[9px] font-bold border border-[#087DF3]/20\">\n                        {p}\n                      </span>\n                    ))}\n                  </div>\n                ) : (\n                  <span className=\"text-white/25 italic block\">[PENDING_SELECTION]</span>\n                )}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* AI Maturity */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/30 block uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">04_AI_MATURITY</span>\n                {answers.aiJourney ? (\n                  <span className=\"text-white font-bold block text-[11px]\">{answers.aiJourney}</span>\n                ) : (\n                  <span className=\"text-white/25 italic block\">[PENDING_SELECTION]</span>\n                )}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Data & Leadership */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/30 block uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">05_INFRA_GOVERNANCE</span>\n                {answers.dataReadiness || answers.leadershipCommitment ? (\n                  <div className=\"space-y-0.5 text-white font-bold text-[9px] block\">\n                    {answers.dataReadiness && <div className=\"text-emerald-400\">DATA: {answers.dataReadiness}</div>}\n                    {answers.leadershipCommitment && <div className=\"text-purple-400\">LEAD: {answers.leadershipCommitment}</div>}\n                  </div>\n                ) : (\n                  <span className=\"text-white/25 italic block\">[PENDING_SELECTION]</span>\n                )}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Challenge Roadmap */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/30 block uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">06_ROADBLOCK_NODE</span>\n                {answers.biggestChallenge ? (\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                    <span className=\"text-red-400 font-bold block text-[11px]\">{answers.biggestChallenge}</span>\n                    {customChallengeText && (\n                      <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/50 leading-tight italic line-clamp-2\">\"{customChallengeText}\"</p>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n                ) : (\n                  <span className=\"text-white/25 italic block\">[PENDING_SELECTION]</span>\n                )}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      ) : null}\n\n      {/* Compile Loading Screen overlay */}\n      {isCompiling && (\n        <div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-[10000] bg-black/95 backdrop-blur-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center p-6 anim-slide-up\">\n          <div className=\"relative w-24 h-24 mb-6\">\n            <div className=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-4 border-white/5\" />\n            <div className=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-4 border-t-[#087DF3] border-r-transparent animate-spin\" />\n            <div className=\"absolute inset-2 rounded-full border border-[#E98828]/20 animate-pulse\" />\n          </div>\n          <h4 className=\"text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-2 uppercase\">Synthesizing Topology Report</h4>\n          <p className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold text-[#087DF3] h-6 transition-all duration-300 animate-pulse\">\n            {compilingMessages[compilingStep]}\n          </p>\n          <div className=\"w-[200px] h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full mt-4 overflow-hidden relative\">\n            <div \n              className=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#087DF3] to-[#E98828] transition-all duration-300\"\n              style={{ width: `${((compilingStep + 1) / compilingMessages.length) * 100}%` }}\n            />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* Step 7: High-Fidelity Enterprise Blueprint Report Output */}\n      {step === 7 && reportGenerated && (\n        <div className=\"space-y-8 anim-slide-up text-white\">\n          <div className=\"p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#087DF3]/30 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#030d1d] to-[#04060c] flex items-center justify-between shadow-lg\">\n            <div>\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-[#087DF3] uppercase tracking-widest\">VERIFIED COMPLETED ASSESSMENT</span>\n              <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mt-1\">Your Custom GFF AI Blueprint is Synthesized</h3>\n              <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-normal mt-1\">Generated for enterprise gate credential <span className=\"text-[#087DF3] font-bold font-mono\">{answers.email}</span></p>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"hidden sm:block\">\n              <span className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold bg-[#E98828]/15 text-[#E98828] border border-[#E98828]/20 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg\">PORTAL_VERIFIED_SECURE</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 items-stretch\">\n            \n            {/* Score circular dial & assessment metadata */}\n            <div className=\"lg:w-1/3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#030712]/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center relative overflow-hidden group\">\n              <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#087DF3]/5 via-transparent to-[#E98828]/5 pointer-events-none\" />\n              <h3 className=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold text-white/40 mb-6\">Enterprise AI Readiness Score</h3>\n              \n              {/* Circular Score Gauge */}\n              <div className=\"relative w-40 h-40 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\">\n                <svg className=\"w-full h-full transform -rotate-90\">\n                  <circle cx=\"80\" cy=\"80\" r=\"70\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\" strokeWidth=\"10\" fill=\"transparent\" />\n                  <circle\n                    cx=\"80\"\n                    cy=\"80\"\n                    r=\"70\"\n                    stroke=\"url(#gradientScore)\"\n                    strokeWidth=\"10\"\n                    fill=\"transparent\"\n                    strokeDasharray=\"440\"\n                    strokeDashoffset={440 - (440 * score) / 100}\n                    strokeLinecap=\"round\"\n                    className=\"transition-all duration-1000 ease-out\"\n                  />\n                  <defs>\n                    <linearGradient id=\"gradientScore\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                      <stop offset=\"0%\" stopColor=\"#087DF3\" />\n                      <stop offset=\"100%\" stopColor=\"#E98828\" />\n                    </linearGradient>\n                  </defs>\n                </svg>\n                <div className=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center\">\n                  <span className=\"text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white\">{score}</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40\">/ 100 SCORE</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Score Category Badge with Custom Glows */}\n              <div className=\"px-5 py-2 rounded-full border border-[#087DF3]/40 bg-[#087DF3]/15 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(8,125,243,0.2)] text-xs font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                {category}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Recommended solution & modelled business impact */}\n            <div className=\"lg:w-2/3 flex flex-col justify-between gap-6\">\n              {/* Recommended GFF Solution */}\n              <div className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#030712]/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 space-y-3 relative overflow-hidden\">\n                <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[150px] h-[150px] bg-[#087DF3]/5 rounded-full blur-[50px] pointer-events-none\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-[#087DF3]\">RECOMMENDED GFF AI SOLUTION</span>\n                <h4 className=\"text-lg md:text-xl font-extrabold text-white flex items-center gap-2\">\n                  {solution.title}\n                </h4>\n                <p className=\"text-xs md:text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed\">\n                  {solution.description}\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Expected Business Impact */}\n              <div className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#030712]/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 space-y-3 relative overflow-hidden\">\n                <div className=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#087DF3] to-[#E98828]\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-[#E98828]\">EXPECTED BUSINESS IMPACT (MODELLED)</span>\n                <p className=\"text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-white/90 leading-normal\">\n                  {impact.metric}\n                </p>\n                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/45 leading-relaxed font-mono italic\">\n                  {impact.disclaimer}\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Custom roadblocked parameter contextual widget */}\n          {customChallengeText && (\n            <div className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030712]/30 p-6 space-y-3\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-mono font-bold text-white/40 block\">Your custom roadblock context details</span>\n              <p className=\"text-xs md:text-sm text-white/70 italic leading-relaxed font-sans\">\n                \"{customChallengeText}\"\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          )}\n\n          {/* Top 5 Recommended AI Opportunities grid */}\n          <div className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#030712]/45 p-6 space-y-4\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-extrabold text-white/40 block tracking-wider\">Synthesized Top 5 Recommended AI Opportunity Nodes</span>\n            <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4\">\n              {opportunities.map((opp, idx) => (\n                <div key={idx} className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.03] transition duration-200 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[145px]\">\n                  <div>\n                    <span className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold text-[#087DF3] block mb-2\">NODE_0{idx + 1}</span>\n                    <h5 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white/95 leading-normal\">{opp}</h5>\n                  </div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold mt-4 flex items-center gap-1\">\n                    <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-pulse\" />\n                    ACTIVE\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n              ))}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* 90-Day Sovereign Implementation Roadmap phases */}\n          <div className=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#030712]/45 p-6 space-y-4 relative overflow-hidden\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-extrabold text-white/40 block tracking-wider\">90-Day Sovereign Implementation Roadmap</span>\n            <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative\">\n              \n              {/* Roadmap Step 1 */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-2 relative pl-6 border-l border-[#087DF3]/30\">\n                <div className=\"absolute -left-[6px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#087DF3] shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(8,125,243,0.8)] animate-pulse\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#087DF3] font-mono tracking-wider\">PHASE 1: DAYS 1 - 30</span>\n                <h4 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Ingestion & Security Baseline</h4>\n                <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed\">\n                  Deploy GFF secure edge nodes. Map standard data schemas and establish compliance firewalls tailored to {answers.industry} parameters.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Roadmap Step 2 */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-2 relative pl-6 border-l border-[#E98828]/30\">\n                <div className=\"absolute -left-[6px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#E98828] shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(233,136,40,0.8)]\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#E98828] font-mono tracking-wider\">PHASE 2: DAYS 31 - 60</span>\n                <h4 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Agent Integration & Multi-Agent DAGs</h4>\n                <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed\">\n                  Synthesize the first 2 high-priority agentic topologies to automate {answers.topPriorities[0] || \"operations\"}. Configure human-in-the-loop checkpoints.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Roadmap Step 3 */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-2 relative pl-6 border-l border-emerald-500/30\">\n                <div className=\"absolute -left-[6px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(16,185,129,0.8)]\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-400 font-mono tracking-wider\">PHASE 3: DAYS 61 - 90</span>\n                <h4 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Production Scale & Token Optimization</h4>\n                <p className=\"text-xs text-white/60 leading-relaxed\">\n                  Scale agents to address {answers.topPriorities[1] || \"additional targets\"}. Perform final optimization checks via GFF Operational Dashboard.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Reset / Start Over Button */}\n          <div className=\"pt-4 flex justify-end\">\n            <button\n              type=\"button\"\n              onClick={() => {\n                setStep(1);\n                setAnswers({\n                  industry: \"\",\n                  companySize: \"\",\n                  topPriorities: [],\n                  aiJourney: \"\",\n                  dataReadiness: \"\",\n                  leadershipCommitment: \"\",\n                  biggestChallenge: \"\",\n                  email: \"\",\n                  otp: \"\",\n                  budget: \"\",\n                  geography: \"\",\n                });\n                setCustomChallengeText(\"\");\n                setOtpSent(false);\n                setEnteredOtp(\"\");\n                setReportGenerated(false);\n              }}\n              className=\"px-6 h-[46px] rounded-lg border border-white/10 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5 transition duration-200\"\n            >\n              Reset & Build New Blueprint\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
